review 1:
If you want to try to feel the pleasure of Balinese suckling pig, you have to come here and prove the deliciousness of this dish yourself.
Not too spicy, if you like it spicy, you can ask for more chili sauce.
The price is affordable and the portion is quite large.
Love eating here, because the service is fast and the place is clean.
Always succeed Babi Guling Wijaya
